o-curricular support services for students including: Scholarship and grant resources Career and specialty planning Academic Advising Certifications and verification of education Community service support Site Registrar and Financial aid liaison Healthcare and wellness services  CampusCare Fitness services Orientation and white coat ceremony Personal counseling services Social events and activities Travel Funding for Educational Activities Student government Student interest groups Student facilities and amenities (study rooms, lounges, lockers, white coats, etc.) Students are encouraged to contact the Assistant Dean for Student Affairs with any questions or concerns.  About  Education  Research  Patient Care  Departments  News  Giving INFORMATION FOR: Prospective and Current Students  Faculty & Staff  Alumni & Friends  Patients  Businesses and Community RESOURCES: UIC Directory  Blackboard  Emergency Information  Contact Us  Apply Now  Give  Contact Us Connect with us!    If you have questions, comments, or problems accessing this site, please E-mail the webmaster  © Copyright 2019 University of Illinois College of Medicine   | Privacy Statement College of Medicine | Chicago | Peoria | Rockford | Urbana                                                                                                                                             